pageContext.claim: “The whistleblower came out with his horrible statement about this call, so I really had no choice. I said immediately -- talk about transparency. I said release it, release it immediately. And then, the whistleblower saw it and shifty Schiff saw it, he's a total crook. Schiff saw it, Pelosi saw it, and they said, we've got a problem. We don't want to have anything to do with the whistleblower anymore and the whistleblower disappeared.”
pageContext.analysis: In fact, Democrats said the rough transcript of President Trump's conversation on July 25 with the Ukrainian president bolstered the case for impeachment and proved a quid pro quo.
